Karen who sent us this story directly tells Good News Movement, “He's always positive, and complimentary of everyone's waves, and is a talented singer, guitar player and surfer too.” 

Enjoy, Tommy! 🏄

After half of her face was paralyzed in a car accident 20 years ago, Thailand native Malinda Herman didn’t want to show her face to anyone for some time. Her son bought her a guitar to help her through that difficult period. The now 71-year-old loves singing with her dogs and cat. 😃🎶🐶😺🎵.

'Beautiful Sunday' was written by Daniel Boone. A happy & beautiful Sunday to you all!
(Malinda Herman Official)

node.text: (Rowley, Ma): Mark Collum says he heard a woman screaming for help about in the early hours Sunday morning. Collum called 911 and ran toward the fire to save his neighbor. Twenty years ago Collum had lost his wife and two children to a fire while the fisherman was working. He is glad that he was there at the right place and time. “[There were] flames billowing out the back, smoke filling up the kitchen, and I just grabbed her and took her out. I had a little smoke in my lungs, same with her. So, I just took her outside, and things worked out well, thank God,” Collum told WCVB. His neighbor sustained minor injuries but is expected to fully recover. Image courtesy my friends at WCVB

node.text: 1-year-old twin girls who were born conjoined at the back of their heads have seen each other for the first time and are happily cooing after undergoing an extremely risky separation surgery in Israel's Soroka Medical Centre in the city of Beersheba. The procedure took 12 hours and included the scalp grafts for both... it was a first in the country. The sisters are recovering well and are expected to live normal lives thanks to the medical heroes! ❤ ❤

node.text:
Mexico’s Senate unanimously approved a federal bill banning animal testing for cosmetics making Mexico the 1st country in North America & 41st country in the world to ban cosmetics testing on animals.��

Under this newly minted law, cosmetic research may not include testing on animals including individual cosmetic ingredients or finished cosmetic products nor can it manufacture, market, or import of cosmetics whether their final formulation or any individual ingredients have been tested on animals elsewhere in the world. 
In the US California, Nevada, Illinois, Virginia, Maryland, Maine & Hawaii have similar bans. 4 more states have introduced bills: New Jersey, New York, Oregon & Rhode Island.

node.text: He starts each race suspended by a towel in his mouth, and catapults extraordinarily through the water. The 30-year-old lost his arms when he was a young boy but that's never stopped him. He wants to teach his 2-year-old that anything's possible. In this year's  2020 Summer Paralympics in Tokyo, Tao won the gold medal at the Men’s Butterfly S5 event with a world record of 30.62, the gold medal at the Men’s Backstroke S5 event with a world record of 31.42 & the gold medal at the 50m Freestyle S5. He also won the gold medal at the Mixed 4x50m Freestyle Relay - 20 Points. Congratulations!! 🥳 🏅
